      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup by second analyst; checklist-based verification of boundary conditions, material assignments, and load application.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by a second analyst using a documented checklist covering boundary conditions, material property assignments, contact definitions, and load magnitudes. No discrepancies identified. Peer review documented in study record."
