      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative hardware by trained assembler following surgical technique guide. Sample-to-sample variability in stiffness (CV=4.2%) and yield force (CV=3.8%) characterized and incorporated into validation uncertainty budget."
    },
