      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate COU loading environment; multiple test configurations preferred.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under ASTM F1717 standard protocol at a single compression-bending angle (5 degrees). Only one test condition evaluated; multi-angle or multi-load-path testing not performed. This factor is below required level and is flagged as a limitation of the validation dataset."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions and loading replicate test fixture constraints and applied displacements within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 fixture geometry modeled explicitly; displacement-controlled loading matched to actuator displacement records. Fixture stiffness measured and incorporated as spring boundary condition. Equivalency confirmed by comparing reaction force at fixture attachment to load cell measurements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
