      "rationale": "Stiffness: mean E/uval = 0.84, max = 1.41. Yield force: mean E/uval = 1.02, max = 1.78. Force at 40 mm: mean E/uval = 0.91, max = 1.63. All values below 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences all below 10%. Validation acceptance criteria met for all QoIs."
